		rationale: "i18n abstractions degrade organically: new developer adds bare 'valor NUMERIC(15,2)' column without currency, new agent hardcodes Brazilian holiday in business logic, new endpoint returns bare number for monetary value, new compliance check hardcodes CNPJ requirement outside interface. Semi-annual review catches drift. When expansion arrives: abstractions are intact and validated."
