	{lensId: "lens-typographic-systems-for-dense-interfaces", relation: "complementsWith", context: "TS defines number formatting in UI (tabular figures, pt-BR locale, number formatting for dense tables). IL extends: formatting is locale-aware (pt-BR, es-CO, etc). TS provides formatting infrastructure (tabular figures, alignment); IL provides locale parameter that drives which format is used."},
